title: Nick Cannon Presents: Future Superstars
overview: Nick Cannon Presents: Future Superstars takes viewers on a coast-to-coast journey during the Future Superstars Tour 2023, the docuseries showcases the remarkable talents of nine emerging artists: Big Boss Vette, DW Flame, Hitman Holla, JD McCrary, Jilly, Klondike Blonde, Pop Money, Symba and Trae Two Three. These artists are on the cusp of making their mark in the music industry, and each episode delves into their unique musical gifts and personal journeys. The series culminates with a finale that looks back at the artists' progression throughout the season.
